description: A data model for DevOps code concerns

objects.baseSearch: `github_webhooks` NOT (action="created" OR action="deleted") NOT (eventtype="GitHub::Issue::Comment" OR eventtype="GitHub::Issue") AND (eventtype="GitHub::Repo" OR eventtype="GitHub::Push") `extract_branch_issuenumber` `individual_commits`

calculations.expression: if((('eventtype'=="GitHub::PullRequest" OR 'eventtype'=="GitHub::PullRequest::Review") AND isnotnull('number')), 'number', if((('eventtype'=="GitHub::PullRequest" OR 'eventtype'=="GitHub::PullRequest::Review") AND isnull('number')), 'pull_request.number', "N/A"))
